{"tid":564950,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［淘寶］麻辣薯粉","createTime":"2018-02-18T13:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T05:57:34.000Z","uid":73909,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2edf920892a786e245ba4c84134c20fc01dd43","tid":564950,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"本身鍾意食煙煙韌韌嘅嘢 又鍾意食辣<br />\n所以試下淘麻辣紅薯粉嚟試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/214002_8aa806565b817e77a74a2f3c61a236e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F214002_8aa806565b817e77a74a2f3c61a236e5.png&h=ac8ce7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/214054_d8bf07b3db7a18820d2df24266aa7442.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F214054_d8bf07b3db7a18820d2df24266aa7442.png&h=d32e3d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/214100_2db8a38301ed876dbeb6ae015c9c71b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F214100_2db8a38301ed876dbeb6ae015c9c71b5.png&h=aefa3e75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/214531_4f5e2bcf7a328794e57c485dc51808da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F214531_4f5e2bcf7a328794e57c485dc51808da.png&h=0d32cd7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/214110_1fd3cfd93091eeec1d63efea5ed6b681.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F214110_1fd3cfd93091eeec1d63efea5ed6b681.png&h=6f0f3452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻同辣都夠 薯粉都夠煙韌 但唔知係咪我落得多水  食啲粉個時好似冇乜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又可能本身啲粉冇味<br />\n同埋本身跟咗包醋 可以變做酸辣粉 但我唔食酸辣粉 所以扔咗<br />\n仲有兩包 下次落返少啲水先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841c8fb3575bdc76125e90d5505b8b0084678cda","tid":564950,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"狗推開 .gif"},{"pid":"f90ae44433488950e994eed73a14584317d7fffa","tid":564950,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"又玩人體鍊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61d390bbf7a90a5935b2eabf1efea2b35581d96","tid":564950,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"841c8fb3575bdc76125e90d5505b8b0084678cda","tid":564950,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"狗推開 .gif"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/2if3mFn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2if3mFn&h=b0f9bdee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"334f85367cc5ccce77a5fa9a43235cc26fb1e34d","tid":564950,"uid":167757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主，good luck"},{"pid":"29ab109012e4fcce820ec1e2210ac9668b0c0fd3","tid":564950,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"334f85367cc5ccce77a5fa9a43235cc26fb1e34d","tid":564950,"uid":167757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主，good luck"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":